Information on testing anf intergration
Part of the importance of testing and Intergration is because it helps verify
that the systems meets the functional requirements and works as expected


### Why Perform Integration Testing?

- Incompatibility between software modules can cause errors
- Developers must confirm that every software module can interact with the database
- Requirements change, thanks to client input.
- Every software developer has their understanding ad programming logic

### An example of test Case Description
The objective is to validate the log-in and the mailbox's module interface link
The description would be "Enter the required log-in credentials and click the log-in button"


